    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一夜的悲伤饮酒后，我们的外星英雄发现自己从宇宙飞船上跌了下来。现在，轮到你来引导他回到安全地带！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>简约与挑战相遇</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你只能使用“W”和“空格键”。没有左右或后退的移动，每一次跳跃都是对精准和耐心的考验。准备好频繁跌倒吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>征服两个独特的关卡：地球和宇宙</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301410/extras/3bcd2038ff7894df0d0408a5154e317d.avif?t=1737098521\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301410/extras_big/3bcd2038ff7894df0d0408a5154e317d.avif?t=1737098521 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>让人生气的游戏玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好迎接一场令人既沮丧又好笑的体验吧！每次跳跃都有搞笑的音效伴随，背景音乐又烦人又容易上瘾，很快变得重复，你会在攀爬的过程中既笑又怒!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>精神挑战在等待着你</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drunk Alien 不仅仅是关于向上攀爬；它还关于掌控你的挫败感并磨练你的技能。它旨在挑战你的极限，让胜利更加令人满足。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301410/extras/c46a11d5d3627aeb55b58139d29aaeed.avif?t=1737098521\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301410/extras_big/c46a11d5d3627aeb55b58139d29aaeed.avif?t=1737098521 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>你能帮他回去吗？加入 Drunk Alien，一起踏上这段不可预测的旅程，每一次跳跃都至关重要，每一次跌倒都是乐趣的一部分。你会帮助他重新夺回在星空中的位置吗？准备迎接一场让你欢呼胜利或陷入绝望的挑战吧!</i></strong></p>",
